-0-948934-00-1}}\n*{{cite book\n  |first1=J |last1=Joyce\n  |first2=J S |last2=King\n  |first3=G |last3=Newman\n  |title=British Trolleybus Systems\n  |publisher=Ian Allan\n  |year=1986\n  |isbn=978-0-7110-1647-7\n  |ref=harv}}\n*{{cite book\n  |first=Charles\n  |last=Klapper\n  |title=The Golden Age of Tramways\n  |publisher=David & Charles\n  |year=1974\n  |isbn=978-0-7153-6458-1\n  |ref=harv\n  |url-access=registration\n  |url=https://archive.org/details/goldenageoftramw0000klap\n  }}\n*{{cite book\n  |first=Keith |last=Turner\n  |title=The Directory of British Tramways\n  |publisher=Patrick Stephens\n  |year=1996\n  |isbn=978-1-85260-549-0\n  |ref=harv}}\n{{refend}}\n\n==External links==\n{{commonscategory|Buses in Essex}}\n*[http://www.sct61.org.uk/ixoss.htm SCT'61 website] - photos and descriptions of Southend-on-Sea trolleybuses and early motorbuses\n*[http://www.sct61.org.uk/hist3.htm Southend Corporation Transport: The Trolleybus Network 1925 to 1954] - a short history\n*[http://www.trolleybus.co.uk/archive/ National Trolleybus Archive]\n*[http://www.britishtrolley.org.uk/ British Trolleybus Society], based in Reading\n*[http://www.trolleybus.co.uk/nta National Trolleybus Association], based in London\n\n{{Historic UK Trolleybuses}}\n\n[[Category:Transport in Southend-on-Sea]]\n[[Category:Defunct trolleybus systems by city|Southend-on-Sea]]\n[[Category:Trolleybus transport in the United Kingdom|Southend-on-Sea]]\n", "name_user": "Bob1960evens", "label": "safe", "comment": "\u2192\u200eHistory:typo", "url_page": "//en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Trolleybuses_in_Southend-on-Sea"}
